        public LockingStrategy getLockingStrategy(Lockable lockable,
                                 LockMode lockMode)
        Returns a no-op locking strategy for all lock modes which will raise an exception upon lock retrieval. Dialects may override this method to provide support for those lock modes they can handle.
        Specified by:
        getLockingStrategy in interface GridDialect
        Parameters:
        lockable - Static meta-data describing a lockable type
        lockMode - A lock mode
        Returns:
        A locking strategy for the given lockable and lock mode or null if this dialect does not support the specified lock mode
